abstract: Many limited-edition 'masstige' collections, in which high-end designers produce lower-priced clothing and accessories for discount retail stores, are selling for extremely inflated resale prices online and in consignment shops.
snippet: Short-lived collaborations between designers and discount stores have produced inflated resale prices online and in consignment shops.
lead_paragraph: Short-lived collaborations between designers and discount stores have produced inflated resale prices online and in consignment shops.
